ingredients: ENRICHED UNBLEACHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, SUGAR, SUGARCANE FIBER, MODIFIED WHEAT STARCH, INULIN, WHEAT GLUTEN. CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF EACH OF THE FOLLOWING: HONEY, DURUM FLOUR, SOYBEAN OIL, SALT, YEAST, GUAR GUM, DATEM, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (PRESERVATIVE), WHITE DISTILLED VINEGAR, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, MONOGLYCERIDES WITH CITRIC ACID PRESERVATIVE, WHEAT FLOUR, ENZYMES, CALCIUM SILICATE, HIGH OLEIC CANOLA OIL.
